{"tid":2159143,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"港府APP追蹤用戶 安排檢測  專家恐發展成另類健康碼 標籤市民","createTime":"2020-08-16T06:50:38.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-17T02:09:53.000Z","uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"6942c5d2459988fcb2fcc8e797ca39b291c3f283","tid":2159143,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-16T06:50:38.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200815/SLSTW6LIHZGZFLOAKWF5CFOH6Y/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200815%2FSLSTW6LIHZGZFLOAKWF5CFOH6Y%2F&d=lmKMjREij7Lxzb1c6qtKJGt2mj8CN1oGBszRVJtr96Q%3D&h=2d9ab62b\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200815%2FSLSTW6LIHZGZFLOAKWF5CFOH6Y%2F&h=dfef76c9\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200815/SLSTW6LIHZGZFLOAKWF5CFOH6Y/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n港府APP追蹤用戶 安排檢測 <br />\n專家恐發展成另類健康碼 標籤市民<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/BIpeRJSUs2NfFwu2vEMYjAM8xM4=/2658x1772/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/HOGCWO5WSVFNFEEPJPHZ6ARFFA.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FBIpeRJSUs2NfFwu2vEMYjAM8xM4%3D%2F2658x1772%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FHOGCWO5WSVFNFEEPJPHZ6ARFFA.jpg&h=05fc7dba&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■港府承認發招標文件，徵求開發商助建應用程式以追蹤社區傳播鏈。<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】第三波疫情出現大量無源頭個案，當局追蹤社區。。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n政府資訊科技總監辦公。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n方保僑：概念猶如智慧燈柱<br />\n<br />\n香港資訊科技商會榮譽會長方保僑指，據他了解政府計劃推行的應用程式，概念猶如智慧燈柱，以地標做法讓市民自願掃描QR Code。市民在手機安裝應用程式後，到商場或食肆時就掃描該處的二維碼，程式會記下有關地址資料。。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n方保僑表示，理論上中央系統不會儲存用戶行蹤，但執行成效要視乎有多少人使用，包括餐廳和商場是否張貼二維碼，市民亦未必會主動「周圍掃」。<br />\n<br />\n他亦憂慮新程式日後或會發展成有健康碼成份在內，類似澳門「澳康碼」的「港康碼」，以綠色、黃色和紅色分辨不同市民的健康情況，本來只適用於過關，但如在澳門不少商場和餐廳會要求市民出示相關條碼才能進入，造成標籤效應。他促請當局推出前，應詳細交代程式與健康碼的關係。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n醫學界：只能當輔助角色<br />\n<br />\n呼吸系統專科醫生梁子超認為，有關應用程式只能擔當輔助角色，不能完全取代個案追蹤緊密接觸者的工作。而商場每天人流多，未必每名市民與確診者有近距離接觸，並暴露在病毒感染風險，若推送相關資訊至每名曾到訪市民，只會造成虛驚。<br />\n<br />\n香港餐。。。。。。。。。。"},{"pid":"3aff5dadc2e3cfe885fbcdd82b7422ffa7fb9faa","tid":2159143,"uid":137493,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-16T06:55:17.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"6e155701901261eca3684507e46607c567da40e1","tid":2159143,"uid":245849,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-16T07:36:03.000Z","msg":"新疆化"},{"pid":"3595f7454585c4309fb7733a246358c6702a5044","tid":2159143,"uid":304769,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-16T10:46:29.000Z","msg":"（正視聽）戴口罩、暫停聚集係值得鼓勵，但係強制戴口罩on9惡法同限聚惡法係一定要反<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2159357\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2159357</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"4ae4c2d5f4b03f529a1ec3da48108c43c39ed697","tid":2159143,"uid":117399,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-17T02:09:53.000Z","msg":"仆街建華已經做緊<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/105907754159242/posts/312899910126691/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F105907754159242%2Fposts%2F312899910126691%2F&d=lmKMjREij7Lxzb1c6qtKJGt2mj8CN1oGBszRVJtr96Q%3D&h=eb1e1389\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/105907754159242/posts/312899910126691/</a>"}]}